{
  "stem": "20581.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I thought, I'll come to this country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It'll be more time with the family, I'll find some family people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it didn't work out in there, so-- my wife wanted to be in here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I says, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I decided to come in here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean, how?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- I came to the HIAS, to the immigration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had papers, my uncle send me an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never wanted to use it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then, later on, when I decided to, I wanted to-- to-- then I used the affidavit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a matter of fact, when the-- when I decided to go to America, a lot of Israeli people were not too happy about it, the people I worked with.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Especially this guy, Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He later became-- he was a [INAUDIBLE] man in the Jewish agency.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he liked me very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one night, he came down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He found out that we want to go for-- to the States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he sat down with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he says to me, listen, [INAUDIBLE], he said, I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, I don't care who goes, where they go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the way, what you did, you contribute so much to the Berihah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, it's really a shame to lose you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, I'll tell you what I'll offer you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says-- we already-- on that time, that's in 1948, when the state was born.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We already had legal immigration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were already taking out people-- we were-- by planes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had air flights from Salzburg to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He says, if you want to, he says, [INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
